data.description: Move right in! This GRETNA ranch home is perfectly located close to Nebraska Crossing, Interstate access, schools, dining & more. This home has been carefully taken care of and beautifully updated. Updates include painted doors/trim, ceramic tile, LVP flooring, and a shiplap linear fireplace to name a few. The finished basement has a large mother-in-law suite connected to a walk-in closet and bathroom. There’s even more to enjoy outdoors; a huge, private backyard with NO rear neighbors, a complete privacy fence, 8x12 storage shed and professional landscaping that stuns. Plus, a sun-room to enjoy it all from! Gretna Schools.
